                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#FFFFFF"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> I don't think they had to change pathing or agro and screw us over. If other classes are mad that we get more xp than they do the only think SOE had to do was give groups a better xp bonus. Having groups give more exp than soloing  would appease group classes, still give us a way of grinding, and it would have taken a lot less time to script. ;) Mosty importantly, it would have kept the game fun for us.  The necro class is a perfect fit for me and a lot of other people because I don't have endless hours to find a group and hunt. With the necro I can log on, kill for an hour or two and log out with some aa or reg exp. I don't have two hours to waste on finding a group that will take a necro. I'm going to wait to see if they fix or change any of this patch and if they don't I'll probably stop playing eq.<br /><br />61 Warlock</span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
